### `++drop`

Unit to list

Makes a ++list of the unwrapped value (`u.a`) of a `++unit` `a`.

Accepts
-------

`a` is a unit.

Produces
--------

A list.

Source
------

    ++  drop                                                ::  enlist
      |*  a/(unit)
      ?~  a  ~
      [i=u.a t=~]


Examples
--------

    > =a ((unit @) [~ 97])
    > (drop a)
    [i=97 t=~] 
    > =a ((unit @) [~])
    > (drop a)
    ~



